data.description:
Location, Location, Location.  This beautiful townhome is centrally located to shopping , entertainment, DIA, DTC and downtown Denver.   This lovely home comes with 3 bedrooms, a loft, 2 full bathrooms and 1/4 bathroom on the main floor.  The townhome also has a 2 car garage on the back of the building.
Upon entering the home, you will see an open floor plan with vinyl plank floors, and 9 foot ceilings. The kitchen comes with all stainless steel appliances and a beautiful quartz countertop.  For those spring and summer days , there is also outdoor space on the side of the home. 
This home is very well kept and is only 3 years old.  This home has everything , except you!!
